<%- include('./partials/header') %>

<main
  class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900 via-[#1a237e] to-[#0d1437]"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="pt-32 lg:pt-40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
      <h1
        class="text-[#7FFFD4] font-raleway text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold mb-6"
      >
        About This Project
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white/90 text-xl max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Welcome to Odysseus Insights, a passion project aimed at making travel
        planning more accessible and enjoyable for everyone. Currently in active
        development, this platform combines AI technology with real-time travel
        data to help you plan your next adventure.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      <!-- Current State Section -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8">
        <div
          class="bg-[#7FFFD4]/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-code text-3xl text-[#7FFFD4]"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Current State</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As a work in progress, Odysseus Insights currently offers basic but
          valuable travel planning features. The platform can generate quick
          itineraries, provide weather updates, and offer insights for your
          chosen destination using AI technology.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          This is a continuously evolving project, developed in my spare time
          with the goal of helping travelers make informed decisions about their
          trips. While it's still growing, I hope these initial features can
          already add value to your travel planning process.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Future Vision Section -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8">
        <div
          class="bg-[#7FFFD4]/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-road text-3xl text-[#7FFFD4]"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          Future Development
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The journey is just beginning! I'm actively working on integrating
          more APIs and features to enhance the travel planning experience.
          Future updates will aim to provide even more comprehensive travel
          insights and practical tools.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          Your feedback and suggestions are valuable in shaping the development
          of this platform. As a solo developer, I'm committed to gradually
          building features that bring real value to travelers and families.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Current Features -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16">
      <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
        <i class="fas fa-robot text-[#7FFFD4] text-2xl mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
          AI Travel Planning
        </h3>
        <p class="text-white/60">
          Get quick, AI-generated itineraries based on your preferences and
          travel dates
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
        <i class="fas fa-cloud-sun text-[#7FFFD4] text-2xl mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Weather Insights</h3>
        <p class="text-white/60">
          Check weather forecasts for your destination to help with trip
          planning
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
        <i class="fas fa-calculator text-[#7FFFD4] text-2xl mb-4"></i>
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Cost Estimation</h3>
        <p class="text-white/60">
          Get rough estimates of travel costs to help with your budget planning
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Development Note -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-[#7FFFD4] text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
        A Note from the Developer
      </h3>
      <p class="text-white/70 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Thank you for checking out Odysseus Insights! This project is my way of
        combining my passion for technology and travel. While it's still in
        development, I hope these tools can already help make your travel
        planning a bit easier. Stay tuned for more features and improvements!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
